entries.title: Cheaters Hacked an AI Bot—and Beat the 'Rocket League' Elite
entries.description: Expert players of the popular vehicular soccer game have been caught out by lesser players using a superhuman bot built on cutting-edge machine learning.

entries.title: A Damning US Report Lays Bare Amazon’s Worker Injury Crisis
entries.description: Investigators found that conditions in three of the company’s facilities risk “serious physical harm” to workers.
